com.xilinx.rapidwright.design

Class Port

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.design.Port
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public class Port
extends Object
implements Serializable, Cloneable
    This class represents the ports used to define the interfaces of modules. They consist of a unique name and the SitePinInst to which they are connected.
    See Also:
